### `packages/utils/`
```
src/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ otp.ts             в†ђ generateOTP(): 6-digit crypto-random string
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ qr.ts              в†ђ encodeQRPayload(tokenId, expiresAt): HMAC-signed base64 string
в”‚                         decodeQRPayload(payload, secret): verifies + returns tokenId
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ eta.ts             в†ђ estimateWaitMinutes(position, avgServiceTimeMs): simple linear estimate
в””в”Ђв”Ђ geo.ts             в†ђ haversineDistance(lat1, lng1, lat2, lng2): km distance
package.json           в†ђ { "name": "@spotly/utils" }
```

